    <li><strong>Get Organized:</strong> Finally, you&rsquo;ll need to establish and maintain an organizational system. <a href="https://www.brother-usa.com/home-office-organization-tips" class="link link-arrow">Read our Home Office Organization Guide</a>&nbsp;to ensure there&rsquo;s a place for everything and everything&rsquo;s in its place.  </li>
